relationships among those countries and we hope it will lead to an
improvement on the situation along that common border," he added.
</P>
<P>
Burns expressed his disagreement on press comments on a meeting
between President Jiang Zeming and Russian President Boris
Yeltsin, which the press comments called was "some kind of
face-off with the United States."
</P>
<P>
"That's not how we see it." he said. 
