<HEADLINE> Greece, U.S. Increase Cooperation in Combating Crime </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, April 24 (Xinhua) -- Greece and the United States have
started their cooperation in dealing with organized crime with the
arrival of a U.S. team of experts for an exchange of experience,
scientific data and methods in this regard.
</P>
